      <title>报道称美国众议院议长与台湾领导人通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/us-house-speaker-holds-call-with-taiwan-s-leader-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国之音报道，美国众议院议长迈克·约翰逊与台湾总统赖清德进行了通话，此举很可能为中国加强对台湾民主国家的军事恐吓增添理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/us-house-speaker-holds-call-with-taiwan-s-leader-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 02:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行行长 Rhee 称波动性将缓慢降至动荡前的水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/bok-rhee-expects-volatility-to-cool-slowly-to-pre-turmoil-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行行长李昌镛表示乐观，认为戒严动乱引发的市场波动将逐渐降温，除非出现新的冲击。他继续努力安抚那些对韩国经济前景持怀疑态度的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/bok-rhee-expects-volatility-to-cool-slowly-to-pre-turmoil-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 02:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
