    <item>
      <title>加州学校发生枪击案 5 岁和 6 岁儿童受伤，枪手死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-04/urgent-shooting-at-northern-california-elementary-school-and-suspect-is-dead-sheriff-s-department-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加利福尼亚州巴勒莫（美联社）——警长官员称，周三，加利福尼亚州北部一所小型宗教 K-8 学校发生枪击案，造成两名儿童受伤，警员赶到现场时发现枪手倒在操场附近的地上，似乎是开枪自杀后死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-04/urgent-shooting-at-northern-california-elementary-school-and-suspect-is-dead-sheriff-s-department-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 22:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国动乱冲击美国亚洲联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korean-turmoil-strikes-at-heart-of-us-alliances-in-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统可能因试图实施戒严而遭到弹劾，这可能会破坏美国主导的东亚联盟，从而影响美国在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普领导下对中国加大施压的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korean-turmoil-strikes-at-heart-of-us-alliances-in-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
