      <title>六小时戒严如何改变震惊的韩国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/how-six-hours-of-martial-law-reshaped-a-stunned-south-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，一个气温接近零度的夜晚，快到晚上 10 点的时候，记者中间开始流传谣言，说韩国总统尹锡烈计划在深夜宣布消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/how-six-hours-of-martial-law-reshaped-a-stunned-south-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国戒严混乱的背后原因及其重要性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/what-s-behind-south-korea-s-martial-law-chaos-will-yoon-be-impeached</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12 月 3 日，韩国领导人宣布戒严，这是韩国近 40 年来首次宣布戒严，引发了一场政治危机。大约六小时后，韩国总统尹锡烈在议会罕见全票通过要求解除戒严令的决议后，撤销了戒严令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/what-s-behind-south-korea-s-martial-law-chaos-will-yoon-be-impeached</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 03:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
